---
---
<section class="section contact-section" id="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-inner">
      <div class="contact-left">
        <p class="section-label">✦ Let's Work Together</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">LANGSUNG<br/>HUBUNGI<br/>SAYA</h2>
        <div class="title-underline"></div>
        <p class="contact-note">
          Harga menyesuaikan kebutuhan project kamu. Ceritain dulu aja, nggak ada yang terlalu susah.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-right">
        <div class="contact-card brutalist-card">
          <div class="contact-icon">💬</div>
          <h3>Chat via WhatsApp</h3>
          <p>Respon cepat, langsung diskusi kebutuhan project kamu.</p>
          <a
            href="https://wa.me/62xxxxxxxxxx?text=Halo%20Raden%2C%20saya%20mau%20konsultasi%20project"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="btn btn-primary wa-btn"
          >
            <span>WhatsApp Sekarang</span>
            <span class="wa-arrow">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-tags">
          <span class="tag">⚡ Fast Response</span>
          <span class="tag">✓ Revisi Included</span>
          <span class="tag">🔒 Privasi Terjaga</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.contact-section {
  border-top: 3px solid var(--border-color);
}
.contact-inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 4rem;
  align-items: center;
}
.section-label {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  display: block;
}
.title-underline {
  width: 60px;
  height: 4px;
  background: var(--accent);
  margin-top: 0.75rem;
  border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.contact-note {
  color: var(--text-muted);
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  max-width: 380px;
}
.contact-card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.contact-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; }
.contact-card h3 {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  font-weight: 700;
}
.contact-card p {
  color: var(--text-muted);
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.wa-btn {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 1rem;
  width: 100%;
  text-align: left;
}
.wa-arrow { font-size: 1.2rem; }
.contact-tags {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 0.75rem;
}
.tag {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
  border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
  box-shadow: 3px 3px 0 var(--shadow-color);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .contact-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
}
</style>
